All I want from you is one code name.

819
01:28:07,616 --> 01:28:09,026
阿勒莱恩
Alleline.

820
01:28:11,286 --> 01:28:12,901
锅匠
Tink er.

821
01:28:13,622 --> 01:28:15,078
